2001-01-14  Boian Bonev  <boian@bonev.com>

    * ext/vpopmail/README:
    * ext/vpopmail/php_vpopmail.c
      ext/vpopmail/php_vpopmail.h: merged my version with David Croft's
    removed unneccessary php.ini calls and defines
